  m_text: "<b>How to use this example:</b>\n1. Make sure you have imported '<i>Mirror</i>\"
    network package\n2. Make a build and run it on two different devices\n3. Connect
    both devices to the same Wi-Fi network\n4. After launching the application on
    the first device, in the upper left corner, click the button \u201C<i>Host (Server
    + Client)</i>\n5. On the second device, enter the address of the first device
    and press the button \u201C<i>Client</i>\u201D\n6. Move two players close to
    each other to hear the conversation."
  m_isRightToLeft: 0
  m_fontAsset: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 8f586378b4e144a9851e7b34d9b748ee, type: 2}
